A 3 year old girl has died after she was burnt beyond recognition in a shack fire in Verulam, in Kwaulu Natal this morning.Reaction Unit South Africa paramedics were called out to the scene by residents reporting a fire. When they arrived they found the shack completely burnt out. The burnt body of the child was found among the wreckage.It was established that the girl was asleep in the shack when her aunt decided to go into the main building to have a bath. Members of the public who were walking past the home noticed the shack in flames and attempted to extinguish the blaze with buckets of water.It could not be established if the fire was caused by a burning candle or a faulty electrical connection which was supplied from the main building.